## Rule 39 — Confluence scope (non–Rule 32) [CRITICAL]

- Default: ticket text + **linked Confluence URLs only**; no broad CQL/search unless user asks or PhoenixExpert Q&A requires it
- **Bug** issue type alone does **not** grant broad wiki search outside **`bug-validator`**
- Cross-dep: **shallow** Confluence only (**`.cursor/skills/cross-dependency-finder/SKILL.md`**)

Violation is a **MUST**.

